The `set grid` command allows grid lines to be drawn on the plot.

Syntax:
@example
      set grid @{@{no@}@{m@}xtics@} @{@{no@}@{m@}ytics@} @{@{no@}@{m@}ztics@}
               @{@{no@}@{m@}x2tics@} @{@{no@}@{m@}y2tics@}
